'''Sonic grenades''',<ref name="Absolutely Everything You Need to Know">''[[Star Wars: Absolutely Everything You Need to Know]]''</ref> also known as '''sonic detonators''',<ref name="A New Dawn">[[A New Dawn (novel)|''A New Dawn'']]</ref> were rare and [[Death|deadly]]<ref name="KoF">''[[Knights of Fate]]''</ref> sonic-based explosive weapons. The [[Bith]] had such sensitive [[Ear|hearing]] that the sound of such grenades could make their heads explode.<ref name="Absolutely Everything You Need to Know" /> The grenades were very powerful, and had the capability to shatter thick [[glass]], crack [[ferrocrete]], and crumple light alloys. Models of sonic grenades included the [[Krupx Munitions]] [[Groundshaker 7]] and the [[Imperial Munitions]] [[M880 Sonic Grenade]].<ref name="KoF" />

